item.description:
Background Within 2 was a project I worked on with Meyer Sound, The Berkeley Center for New Media, and Artist Tarek Atoui. We started with the question of &ldquo;How do we create music for the hearing impaired?&rdquo; A quote by Stanford Professor Anne Fernald guided me throughout the project:
 &ldquo;Sound is touch at a distance.&rdquo;
 How can we rethink music in such a way that brings it to a more visceral physical sensation?
